skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: urban oracle
des:
Welcome to the Urban Oracle.

You can ask the Urban Oracle any question and she will answer! Your question can be about the future, the past, popular culture or pretty much anything you can think of and she will answer!

To get started simply say "Alexa, open Urban Oracle" or "Alexa, ask Urban Oracle" followed by any question you can think of.


*Answers may not be entirely accurate 

*This is my first attempt at a skill for Alexa, if you find any bugs please feel free to email me

***This is just intended to be a bit of fun, please don't take it to seriously

****SL Mobile cannot be held responsible for any offence caused by this skill
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
